          consequatur atque dolorum laboriosam ullam.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    {{!=================== ABOUT SECTION START ======================}}



    {{!=================== FOOTER SECTION START ======================}}
    <footer class="container-fluid text-center bg-black text-white py-3">
      <h6>Copyright &#169 ServiceHub, Pune, Maharashtra 411 041</h6>
    </footer>
    {{!=================== FOOTER SECTION END ======================}}

  </div>

  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
    integrity="sha384-YvpcrYf0tY3lHB60NNkmXc5s9fDVZLESaAA55NDzOxhy9GkcIdslK1eN7N6jIeHz"
    crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>

</html>